article_title: Hospital wants to cut $17M over two years
article_text:
Cheyenne, WY (82001)

Today

A mix of clouds and sun early, then becoming cloudy later in the day. A stray shower or thunderstorm is possible. High 59F. Winds NNE at 10 to 20 mph..

Tonight

Partly cloudy skies. A stray shower or thunderstorm is possible. Low around 40F. Winds NW at 5 to 10 mph.

article_metadata.author: Becky Orr

og.description: CHEYENNE - Cheyenne Regional Medical Center will start a cost-cutting program in September that hospital leaders hope will save $17 million over two years.
